Why don’t mummies take vacations? Because they’re afraid to unwind.
What’s a ghost’s favorite workout? Deadlifts.
Why did the vampire flunk art class? He could only draw blood.
What’s a skeleton’s favorite instrument? The trom-bone.
How do witches keep their hair in place? With scare-spray.
Why did the zombie stay home from school? He felt rotten.
What do you get when you cross a vampire and a snowman? Frostbite.
Why don’t ghosts like rain? It dampens their spirits.
Why did Dracula become a vegetarian? Because biting necks was just too much at steak.
How do monsters tell their future? With a horror-scope.
What’s a mummy’s favorite type of music? Wrap.
Why did the ghost go to therapy? For his haunting past.
What kind of makeup do witches wear? Mas-scare-a.
Why are skeletons so chill? Nothing gets under their skin.
What do you call a haunted chicken? A poultry-geist.
How do vampires start their letters? "Tomb it may concern..."
What do you call a witch who lives at the beach? A sand-witch.
Why was the jack-o'-lantern afraid to cross the road? It had no guts.
How do ghosts keep fit? By exorcising regularly.
Why did the werewolf get promoted? He was the leader of the pack.
What’s a monster’s favorite dessert? I scream!
Why do ghouls love parties? Because they have a spooktacular time.
Why did the witch open a bakery? She was good at spell-ing.
How do skeletons call their friends? On the tele-bone.
Why don’t zombies ever get lost? They always follow their gut.
What did the ghost say to the bee? Boo-bee!
Why did Frankenstein go to therapy? He had a complex.
What’s Dracula’s least favorite meal? A stake dinner.
Why are graveyards so noisy? Because of all the coffin.
What do ghosts serve at parties? Boos.
Why didn’t the skeleton go to the Halloween party? He had no body to go with.
